Fourth Department,

July, 1991

(July 12, 1991) The People of the State of New York, Respondent, v *560Jose Ramos Burgos, Appellant.

— Judgment unanimously affirmed. Counsel’s application to withdraw granted (see, People v Crawford, 71 AD2d 38). (Appeal from Judgment of Ontario County Court, Henry, Jr., J. — Criminal Sale Controlled Substance, 2nd Degree.) Present — Dillon, P. J., Doerr, Lawton, Lowery and Davis, JJ.
